[[2]]
[1] "gray52"              "N. American_opossum" "Johannesburg"       

[[3]]
[1] "gray18"     "Arctic fox" "Prague"    

[[4]]
[1] "gray30"      "Rock hyrax2" "Manila"     

[[5]]
[1] "burlywood"        "African elephant" "Shanghi"         
```


:::
:::



### `lapply()`



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
l2 <- lapply(
  X = l,               # list input
  FUN = paste,         # function: `paste()`
  collapse = "; "      # additional argument to `paste()`
)

l2
```

