### Function



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
# custom function to
#   1) modify column names 
#   2) add a column

fn <- function(df) {
  colnames(df) <- stringr::str_to_title(colnames(df))
  df |>
    mutate(Action = NA, .before = everything())
}
```
:::



### `lapply()`



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
l2 <- lapply(
  X = l,               # list input
  FUN = fn             # function: `fn()`
)
```
:::


