## `purrr::map()`

:::::: {.panel-tabset}

### Specs

::::: {.columns}
:::: {.column .nonincremental width="50%"}
::: {.nonincremental}

`lapply()`

- Input: a vector or list
- Output: a vector or list
- Arguments:
    + `X`: a vector or list
    + `FUN`: a function
    + `...`: additional arguments to `FUN` (optional)

:::
::::

:::: {.column .nonincremental width="50%"}
::: {.nonincremental}

`map()`

- Input: a vector or list
- Output: a vector or list
- Arguments:
    + `.x`: a vector or list
    + `.f`: a function
    + `...`: additional arguments to `.f` (optional)

:::
::::
:::::

### List



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
l <- list()

for (i in 1:5) {                             # populate a list
  l[[i]] <- c(                               # each element contains:
    sample(colors(), 1),                     #  - a color
    sample(rownames(alr4::brains), 1),       #  - an animal
    sample(rownames(alr4::BigMac2003), 1)    #  - a city
  )
}

l
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[[1]]
[1] "orangered" "Mole rat"  "Madrid"   

[[2]]
[1] "grey41"      "Beaver"      "Los_Angeles"

[[3]]
[1] "gray24"     "Slow loris" "Bangkok"   

[[4]]
[1] "gray21" "Goat"   "Milan" 

[[5]]
[1] "snow"            "Desert hedgehog" "Sao_Paulo"      
```


:::
:::



### Compare use

::::: {.columns}
:::: {.column .nonincremental width="50%"}



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
l2 <- lapply(
  X = l,
  FUN = paste,
  collapse = "; "
)

l2
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[[1]]
[1] "orangered; Mole rat; Madrid"

[[2]]
[1] "grey41; Beaver; Los_Angeles"

[[3]]
[1] "gray24; Slow loris; Bangkok"

[[4]]
[1] "gray21; Goat; Milan"

[[5]]
[1] "snow; Desert hedgehog; Sao_Paulo"
```


:::
:::



::::
:::: {.column .nonincremental width="50%"}



::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
l3 <- map(
  .x = l,
  .f = paste,
  collapse = "; "
)

l3
```

::: {.cell-output .cell-output-stdout}

```
[[1]]
[1] "orangered; Mole rat; Madrid"

[[2]]
[1] "grey41; Beaver; Los_Angeles"

[[3]]
[1] "gray24; Slow loris; Bangkok"

[[4]]
[1] "gray21; Goat; Milan"

[[5]]
[1] "snow; Desert hedgehog; Sao_Paulo"
```


